title: >>> The END of the TURMOIL
body_text:
The end of January is near and there is only one event that has the privelege of closing out this outstanding month ...
Beginning with DODGEBALL 21 back on January 7th, most would agree that January of 2006 was the most unpredictable and unorthodox month in the history of dodgeball. Dates were changed, the most brutal of "Wet Wars", new "age" records, and the return of the Carty brothers, are all contributing factors. DODGEBALL XXIV could certainly add to the turmoil that the month has brought.
~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~
The DODGEBALL 26 poster contest is already underway. Several designs have already been submitted, which is good sign. DODGEBALL 26 remember is not until February 11th, so for anyone still wanting to participate, you do have ample time.
